   "source": [
    "# DNABERT-2 Fine-tuning for 16S Taxonomic Classification\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook fine-tunes DNABERT-2 on NCBI 16S rRNA sequences for species-level taxonomic classification.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime**: ~1-1.5 hours on Colab T4 GPU\n",
    "**Output**: Downloadable model for local inference"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
